ActPublic Sector Pension Investment Board Act
PrecisReappointment of PAUL CANTOR of Toronto, Ontario, as a director of the Public Sector Pension Investment Board to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years; and designation of PAUL CANTOR of Toronto, Ontario, one of the directors of the Board, as Chairperson of the Public Sector Pension Investment Board to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years; effective March 28, 2003.
